  "title": "Retail Sales",
  "description": "<p><strong>Want to join our team?</strong></p>\n<p>To cope with our business expansion, we are inviting candidate to join us!</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Retail Sales Associate by a health service provider and on job training provided.</li>\n  <li>Salary &amp; sales commission are competitive</li>\n  <li>Career Development</li>\n  <li>5.5days work-week</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure merchandise and displays are consistently well presented.</li>\n  <li>Attend to walk in customers and demonstrate products, share health care knowledge according to their needs.</li>\n  <li>Perform daily housekeeping of the store to ensure cleanliness of the store to our customers.</li>\n  <li>To understand the products and the environment in which they are sold, to understand what customers are looking for and to present them in an appropriate way</li>\n  <li>To ensure that physical stock levels are in line with the stock held in the system.</li>\n  <li>Ensure shop cleanliness.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min O Level education</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduated/Non-experience are welcomed. Training will be provided</li>\n  <li>Sales and result-oriented</li>\n  <li>Able to liaise with Mandarin speaking customers.</li>\n  <li>Good customer service skill</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated and a great team player</li>\n  <li>Highly committed and willing to learn healthcare related knowledge</li>\n  <li>Kindness towards elderly</li>\n</ul>",
